  <sect3 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Gnome Tetravex</title>

    <para>
      <application>gnome-tetravex</application> is a
      simple puzzle where pieces must be positioned so 
      that the same numbers are touching each other.
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

